1

Like the machete the snake: Integration of topic and vehicle in poetry comprehension reveals meaning
construction processes

Cristóbal Pagán Cánovas Institute for Culture and Society, University of Navarra, Spain
Javier Valenzuela Dept. Of English Philology, University of Murcia, Spain
Julio Santiago Dept. Of Experimental Psychology, University of Granada, Spain

